45
00:02:33,860 --> 00:02:38,300
It's a neat trick staying exactly where you are while feeling like the voice of reason.

46
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:41,819
The goal, of course, is to become a relic of the self.

47
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,659
A museum devoted to your own past.

48
